Hubway Data Visualization
=========================

These are explorations for the Hubway Data Visualization Challenge. The code is
often crufty for one-off purposes, but do feel free to use it as a reference or
starting point (Apache 2.0 license)


001-basic
---------

A leaflet.js map with CloudMade tiles and the hubway stations added as markers.


002-connections
---------------

A map with the hubway stations linked by lines whose thickness is proportional to the number of rides.


